Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.49,0:00:34.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有时间的黄昏的天空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:38.73,0:00:45.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进行着一段永远的旅程
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.64,0:00:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冰冷的指尖继续探索着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.05,0:01:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,碎片发出光芒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.02,0:01:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,紧紧的抱住胸口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.33,0:01:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,寻找遗失的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.74,0:01:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用双手的掌心确认
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:24.08,0:01:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相遇在新的早晨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.38,0:01:37.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间开始流动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.79,0:02:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪 还没到会面时间唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.36,0:02:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.02,0:02:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的事情已经不用担心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.66,0:02:17.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好好去上学吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.86,0:02:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是毕业典礼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.33,0:02:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…\N已经到了这种季节了呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.30,0:02:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟佑一有好好相处吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.94,0:02:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…有啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.24,0:02:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.21,0:02:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由从我的面前消失之后\N已经过了一个月
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.28,0:02:39.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发生意外的秋子阿姨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.18,0:02:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在则在做复健逐渐复原当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.35,0:02:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.32,0:02:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从那天以来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.62,0:02:49.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和名雪之间就若有似无的\N互相避开对方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.20,0:02:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,季节 走到了春天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.67,0:02:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,「风所到达的地方」
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.38,0:03:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.45,0:03:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佐佑理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.05,0:03:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你毕业了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.82,0:03:15.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.52,0:03:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来很适合你呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.36,0:03:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.39,0:03:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 全身上下都散发出\N高雅文静的淑女气质呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.90,0:03:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然是跟某个粗暴的人\N完全不一样呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.83,0:03:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,痛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.74,0:03:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么\N真的是人要衣装啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.17,0:03:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 说的太过分了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.34,0:03:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有别的话可以说了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.91,0:03:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你毕业了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.82,0:03:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.12,0:03:52.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小舞在不好意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.12,0:03:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛 好痛\N要变矮了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:56.83,0:03:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留学？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.73,0:04:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我们两个决定的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.60,0:04:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那边的学校虽然毕业很难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.20,0:04:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是要进去\N却是非常的简单哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.11,0:04:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…就算是再怎么简单也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.38,0:04:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.41,0:04:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要跟小舞在一起的话 对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.65,0:04:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是要道别了吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.65,0:04:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也不是就不能见面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.96,0:04:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.12,0:04:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:31.00,0:04:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相泽同学可真的是\N不能疏忽大意啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.07,0:04:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,香里！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.27,0:04:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.44,0:04:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,栞 你的身体没问题吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.01,0:04:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 托你的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是什么都没有做喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.38,0:04:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 都是多亏了佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.42,0:04:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然姐姐也有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.82,0:04:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 那种讲法\N好像顺便的一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.56,0:04:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有精神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.43,0:05:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 春天开始\N就可以跟大家一起上学了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.70,0:05:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过因为出席数不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.70,0:05:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以要重读一年级
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.94,0:05:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没问题的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.54,0:05:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种身高就算说是一年级\N也不会有人奇怪的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.94,0:05:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我最讨厌说那种话的人了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.71,0:05:24.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.72,0:05:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.92,0:05:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次跟我一起做雪人好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.79,0:05:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雪人？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.82,0:05:31.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.56,0:05:35.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要做一个最大的\N作为我恢复健康的纪念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.66,0:05:37.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是40公尺高之类的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.73,0:05:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.60,0:05:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别那么肯定啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.10,0:05:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我从小就有的梦想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.43,0:05:45.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为一个人是没办法做\N那么大的雪人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.40,0:05:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,40公尺是不可能的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.44,0:05:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且现在也已经没有积雪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.11,0:05:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以等到下一个冬天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.98,0:05:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意跟我一起做吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.48,0:05:55.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.81,0:05:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.12,0:06:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 事实上…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.99,0:06:04.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.72,0:06:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.53,0:06:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,皮罗几时回来的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.90,0:06:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我从医院回来的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.24,0:06:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它就在门口等着了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.47,0:06:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 这些日子\N到底是跑到哪里去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.61,0:06:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真会让人操心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.31,0:06:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是真是太好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.18,0:06:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为这样一来\N就算佑一不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.48,0:06:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不会那么寂寞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.39,0:06:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,转学？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.89,0:06:39.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨发生了意外对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.39,0:06:42.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像因为那样\N我老妈就觉得很担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.93,0:06:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说还是要住在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.50,0:06:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经决定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.53,0:06:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要搬去的地点也确定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.07,0:06:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.14,0:06:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪她知道吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.04,0:06:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相泽同学要转学这件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.91,0:06:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么都没跟她讲吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.34,0:06:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是有跟她提过…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.38,0:06:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.18,0:07:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易终于可以跟佑一\N一起上同样的学校了说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.95,0:07:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别露出那种表情嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.65,0:07:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放假的时候\N我还会再到这里来玩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.15,0:07:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉会有点寂寞呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.29,0:07:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剪刀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.03,0:07:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.66,0:07:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经…整理的差不多了呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.23,0:07:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该送的东西都送光了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.13,0:07:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.07,0:07:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,车票也弄好了\N后天三点的特快车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.27,0:07:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样…啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.44,0:07:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,转学好像要办很多手续
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.28,0:07:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然很麻烦\N但是在春假结束前…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.05,0:07:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.38,0:07:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要去医院了\N晚餐你自己先吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.43,0:07:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一说 后天就要回家去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.10,0:07:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还说车票也已经买好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.47,0:07:58.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.67,0:08:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一个人没问题吗…？ 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.71,0:08:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.17,0:08:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算没有佑一叫我起床
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.78,0:08:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以自己起床的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.65,0:08:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是那个意思…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.78,0:08:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你小的时候 可是哭的很厉害喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.05,0:08:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你呀 一直哭着说\N叫佑一不要回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.16,0:08:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是几岁的事情？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.39,0:08:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4、5岁的时候吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.63,0:08:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那时候佑一明明说\N放假的时候会再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.27,0:08:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是名雪却还是一直哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.90,0:08:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那样子吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.97,0:08:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.53,0:09:04.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对自己诚实一点吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.24,0:09:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要再勉强忍耐\N把自己的心意全部说出来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.31,0:09:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果对象是佑一的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.94,0:09:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就没有什么不好意思的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.92,0:09:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安！佑一！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.79,0:09:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由…你为什么会在这里…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.47,0:09:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不可以在这里吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.43,0:09:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.84,0:09:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.57,0:09:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在正要做饼干呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.67,0:09:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,饼干？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.88,0:09:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 我还想要把它送给佑一呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.61,0:09:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了啦 一定又会烧焦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.75,0:09:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不会呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.35,0:09:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有认真的\N跟秋子阿姨学了做法呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.35,0:09:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不过学了一下下\N手艺就会变好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.66,0:10:01.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也煮粥煮成功了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.73,0:10:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨也说很好吃\N把粥吃掉了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.20,0:10:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那种话一听就知道是客套话了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.03,0:10:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样好了\N如果看起来好吃的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.10,0:10:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我吃也是可以的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.27,0:10:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.77,0:10:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 我会努力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.32,0:10:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真要命 睡太晚了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.22,0:10:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.23,0:10:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北川…还有香里跟栞也…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.00,0:10:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我叫他们来的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.57,0:10:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是佑一的饯行会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.75,0:10:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,相泽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.81,0:10:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要搬走了\N怎么不早点跟我说啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.05,0:11:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易跟你成为朋友的说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.82,0:11:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会寂寞的耶~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.42,0:11:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起啦！北川\N我忘记跟你说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.46,0:11:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个好好吃~
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.16,0:11:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是栞亲手做的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.00,0:11:17.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个对吧 亲手做的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.07,0:11:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不…不…这个是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.70,0:11:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,赶快拿出来吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.21,0:11:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.57,0:11:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:26.31,0:11:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.85,0:11:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给我的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.28,0:11:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.62,0:11:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手制的围巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.12,0:11:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樱花都已经开了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.82,0:11:38.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,季节完全不合…对吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.13,0:11:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 我会珍惜的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.26,0:11:46.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.76,0:11:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明很高兴的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.47,0:11:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪…为什么眼泪会…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.50,0:11:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是傻瓜呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.67,0:11:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美阪 我也好想要喔\N手制围巾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.17,0:11:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己编吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.31,0:11:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好冷淡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.78,0:12:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去泡咖啡…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.31,0:12:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.91,0:12:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了\N主角坐好就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.95,0:12:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.66,0:12:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 相泽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.06,0:12:15.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还会再见面的对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.86,0:12:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你们 香里 栞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.33,0:12:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.70,0:12:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,北川也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.73,0:12:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毫无诚意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.97,0:12:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.90,0:12:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多保重喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.10,0:12:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该整理整理了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.21,0:12:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.54,0:12:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.01,0:12:36.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为佑一的眼里\N总是只有亚由一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.58,0:12:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.12,0:12:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.05,0:12:42.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.92,0:12:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.36,0:12:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,家里我来整理就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.59,0:12:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你先去医院好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.76,0:12:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想妈妈她在等你吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.23,0:12:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪在躲着我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.23,0:12:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 在躲避的人是我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.94,0:13:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到在两人之间的气氛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.11,0:13:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟是这么的凝重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.81,0:13:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结果 我仍然只是\N一直在伤害名雪吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.18,0:13:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.62,0:13:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…必须要道歉才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.72,0:13:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前 我把名雪送我的雪兔\N弄坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.89,0:13:22.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又糟蹋了她的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.40,0:13:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪她不论过了多久\N都还只是个孩子呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.50,0:13:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她是那种到了现在都还深信着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.23,0:13:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会有白马王子来迎接她的类型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.97,0:13:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是这样的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.17,0:13:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 恋爱\N是为了让人成长而存在的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.91,0:13:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使那份思念没有实现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.88,0:13:47.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是也会累积于生命之中\N不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.56,0:14:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使那份思念没有实现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.20,0:14:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是也会累积于生命之中\N不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.54,0:14:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,累积于生命之中吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.12,0:14:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.59,0:14:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要走了吗…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.99,0:14:32.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 还没有…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.40,0:14:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不送我吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.30,0:14:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 今天妈妈要做检查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.54,0:14:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊…替我向秋子阿姨问好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.71,0:14:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.68,0:14:48.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.78,0:14:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不去给佑一送行好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.19,0:14:59.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 这样就好了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.92,0:15:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也差不多该走了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.53,0:15:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.63,0:15:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这闹钟还没有当面还给名雪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.21,0:15:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊？想吃东西吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.35,0:15:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.95,0:15:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.98,0:15:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望你不要生气听我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.85,0:15:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我 即使到现在\N都还是最喜欢佑一的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.66,0:15:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从七年前就一直一直…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.26,0:15:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.90,0:15:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已经没关系了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.06,0:15:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使佑一不在了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.67,0:15:43.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我完全没有关系哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.55,0:15:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.48,0:16:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 不客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.04,0:16:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.84,0:16:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.11,0:16:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,佑一 现在赶快到医院去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.71,0:16:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊 电车已经…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.45,0:16:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里有一个等着佑一的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.92,0:16:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从七年前开始一直等着…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.39,0:16:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.66,0:16:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.13,0:16:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…那样…名雪 你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.84,0:17:01.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.98,0:17:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是这是第一次\N也是最后一次了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.65,0:17:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,名雪…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.02,0:17:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你…快点去吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.80,0:17:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的 佑一…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.07,0:17:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢流动的景色…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.61,0:17:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,冬天 白雪飞舞的城镇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.42,0:17:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢一边留下新的足迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.88,0:17:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一边在商店街跑着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.29,0:17:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,春天 积雪溶化的城镇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.96,0:17:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢用手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.66,0:17:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将遗落在树木下的小雪球\N捡起来的那一刻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.80,0:18:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夏天 忘却雪的寒冷的城镇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.81,0:18:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢从放在肩膀上的\N伞的缝隙中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.21,0:18:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,望着朦胧的街景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.78,0:18:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秋天 诉说着\N冬天即将到来的城镇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.95,0:18:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢用手去接住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.32,0:18:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个从仰望着的云中\N落下的小小的雪的结晶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.33,0:18:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后季节来到了冬天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.56,0:18:26.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,城镇被雪白的颜色\N所覆盖的季节
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.03,0:18:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢流动的季节…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.97,0:18:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…\N就像在雪中冻结住的水珠一般…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.67,0:18:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的时间也停止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.78,0:18:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在没有季节分别的时间当中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.31,0:18:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都是只有一个人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.58,0:18:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不停的重复…不停的重复…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.95,0:18:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在梦中一直看着相同的景色…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.29,0:18:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把自己托付在\N没有黎明的夜里…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.70,0:19:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是现在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.97,0:19:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,渐渐的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.61,0:19:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夜晚开始泛出了曙光…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.35,0:19:23.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.82,0:19:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好慢 太慢了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.72,0:19:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 那个帽子是怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.16,0:19:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不会笑我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.23,0:19:29.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会笑你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.99,0:19:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会笑我？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.33,0:19:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别看我这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.26,0:19:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好歹我也是个信守约定的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.76,0:19:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明就迟到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.60,0:19:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种说法\N一点说服力都没有啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.97,0:19:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么回事嘛？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.57,0:19:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.94,0:19:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去了理发店剪头发…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.44,0:19:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被剪掉了一大堆…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.08,0:19:48.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你一定会笑的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.31,0:19:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么关系嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.58,0:19:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱啊 看来像个小男生一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.45,0:19:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢 我是女孩子嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.95,0:19:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.25,0:19:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不甘心的话\N就说声「人家」来听听吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.09,0:20:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然很坏心眼…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.96,0:20:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实明明就很温柔的 对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.23,0:20:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 佑一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.67,0:20:14.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啊 突然这样讲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:14.97,0:20:17.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直在呼唤着我的名字吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.04,0:20:20.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我听见佑一的声音了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.72,0:20:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚由 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.69,0:20:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你等了七年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.30,0:20:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会再到任何地方去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.80,0:20:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会一直待在你身边
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.94,0:20:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以亚由\N请你张开眼睛吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.92,0:21:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都在叫我对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.19,0:21:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,叫我的名字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.89,0:21:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是因为佑一一直呼唤着我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.89,0:21:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才醒过来的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.76,0:21:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就叫做奇迹对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.56,0:21:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能像这样再和佑一见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.67,0:21:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.34,0:21:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约好了对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.14,0:21:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说过只要是我能做得到的\N都会帮你实现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.08,0:21:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么 要去吃鲷鱼烧吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.08,0:21:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天气已经变暖和了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.75,0:21:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有人在卖鲷鱼烧了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.38,0:21:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你放心 因为有秋子阿姨会做嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.72,0:21:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲷鱼烧可以自己做吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.52,0:21:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也想做看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.92,0:21:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是算了吧
